OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fmostly fading during this evening,
OL,7,Fleaving a largely dry night with some
OL,8,Fclear spells, especially towards the
OL,9,Feast. The odd spot of rain still
OL,10,Fpossible across the south and west,
OL,11,Fwith perhaps some mist patches also
OL,12,Fdeveloping.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FDry with sunny spells at
OL,15,Ffirst. Cloud will build through the
OL,16,Fafternoon, perhaps with the odd spot
OL,17,Fof light rain. Temperatures around
OL,18,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
