OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FRemaining cool and rather cloudy on
OL,7,FWednesday, with some showers,
OL,8,Fespecially in the west. A little
OL,9,Fwarmer again from Thursday, with a mix
OL,10,Fof sunny spells and occasional showers.
